{"tid":540439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英網紅想宣傳換免費住宿　酒店公開郵件：我粉絲比你多","createTime":"2018-01-25T13:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T18:58:05.000Z","uid":84436,"like":101,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e0efa29c9527d856a660d4d859f56ac9b22d437a","tid":540439,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:08:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/152458/%E8%8B%B1%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E6%83%B3%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%8F%9B%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%BF-%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E9%83%B5%E4%BB%B6-%E6%88%91%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E6%AF%94%E4%BD%A0%E5%A4%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F152458%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%258F%259B%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25AE%25BF-%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2583%25B5%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E6%25AF%2594%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%25A4%259A&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=93cf1ca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/152458/%E8%8B%B1%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E6%83%B3%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%8F%9B%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%BF-%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E9%83%B5%E4%BB%B6-%E6%88%91%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E6%AF%94%E4%BD%A0%E5%A4%9A</a><br />\n<br />\n現在網絡紅人的影響力愈來愈大，不少商業機構都喜歡找他們宣傳產品，不過對於網絡紅人的價值其實也是各花入各眼。英國一名有逾9.5萬訂閱者的Youtuber，早前向愛爾蘭一家酒店要求免費住宿，並表示可以透過自己的社交網絡為酒店宣傳。面對這樣的要求，酒店不但不賣帳，還在facebook公開事件。<br />\n<br />\n英國網紅達比（Elle Darby）Youtube有9.5萬訂閱者，Instagram則有8萬多名追隨者，她早前向酒店發電郵，表示打算在2月與男友到愛爾蘭都柏林旅遊，正在尋找住宿，詢問酒店可否為他們提供免費住宿，她會在社交網絡宣傳酒店作報酬，還表示自己曾與奧蘭多環球影城有過類似合作。<br />\n<br />\n後來收到這電郵的愛爾蘭酒店The White Moose Caf&eacute;在facebook公開電郵內容，但遮蓋了發件人的名字。酒店首先感謝其電郵，指「提出這種要求想必需要很大自尊和勇氣」，酒店反問「如果讓你免費住宿，來換取酒店曝光的話，誰來支付服務你的工作人員呢？誰來支付水、電、暖氣的費用？或者我應該和員工說他們出現在你的影片中代替他們的人工」。<br />\n<br />\n酒店負責人指他們酒店的facebook也有18萬人關注，Snapchat則有逾8萬追隨者，而他本人也是一個博客，負責人指這些數字不代表有權不支付別人需要支付的東西，又建議達比和其他人一樣付款，如果有酒店認為她可以幫忙宣傳，或許能給她免費升級至高級套房。"},{"pid":"db4d7d8eea0e78603e543b55e1ec13ffb1c02810","tid":540439,"uid":128921,"like":30,"dislike":24,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:09:46.000Z","msg":"雖然個YOUTUBER係柒，但酒店都好撚串下"},{"pid":"4903ba9b281bb259d064cd4e1533644bda6d8bd4","tid":540439,"uid":37735,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:09:50.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db85de833eed27e9aa18f67ce7f00ef5d7040ee","tid":540439,"uid":9217,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:11:04.000Z","msg":"垃圾以為自己好出名<br />\n抵俾人串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6c571d2bdfe196b0305f3338adfa2a11f3e741","tid":540439,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"支那01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4399a1c495342b50320cc9be5c20738900b9d8b1","tid":540439,"uid":134421,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:17:07.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地offer就話姐<br />\n自己r同乞有咩分別？"},{"pid":"01008b7a5009b7d80257a8b14d41ce57c65d8834","tid":540439,"uid":34869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"db4d7d8eea0e78603e543b55e1ec13ffb1c02810","tid":540439,"uid":128921,"like":30,"dislike":24,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:09:46.000Z","msg":"雖然個YOUTUBER係柒，但酒店都好撚串下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:19:21.000Z","msg":"個禿伯抵比人串啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77448aaad8ec9fc0e09662688562106bdc4fb273","tid":540439,"uid":4179,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"依家宣傳效果仲好 又可以撚狗<br />\n酒店公關勝<img src=\"/a